Thank you for your interest in Metadata Games.

LICENSE
-------

Metadata Games is available under the GNU Affero General Public
License v3+. For more specific licensing information, see the
top-level file 'LICENSE'.


INSTALLATION
------------

Please consult the install guide in ../documents/mg_guide_install.text or
../documents/mg_guide_install.html to learn more about how to install 
Metadata Games on your server.  


REQUIREMENTS
------------

The minimum requirement for MG is that your Web server supports PHP
5.1.0 or above. MG has been tested under the Apache HTTP server on
Windows and Linux.

On a clean install, please access the following URL to check if your
Web server meets the requirements for MG:

("MGPath" is where MG is installed)

      http://hostname/MGPath/installer.php


The MG Developer Team
